data.description: Don't miss out on this gorgeous home in Riverwalk that has it ALL! Not only does it have 4 spacious bedrooms with the owner's suite downstairs, but it also has a dedicated office space & giant bonus room with a custom Austin city skyline! Did I forget to mention that it has an in-ground pool with rock waterfall feature? And no rear neighbors? Oh, and the elementary school is within walking distance & the bus stop is at the corner. This home is a dream come true, sits on the largest lot in the neighborhood on a partial cul de sac & has a view to downtown Hutto that you can't beat! Located minutes from 130 Toll, Hwy 79, HEB & nestled in Fast-Growing Hutto, get ready to make this home yours! As if this isn't enough, the kitchen has beautiful porcelain tiled flooring, room for all your cooking gadgets, more than 1 cook & oodles of counter top space! The 2 story foyer lets in tons of natural light & the upstairs landing has a quaint reading nook! If you want some space to run around outside, this backyard is an oasis just waiting for your special touch. An extended poured concrete patio surrounds the custom pool and pool house to protect equipment/storage. Can you visualize that yard with a covered pergola poolside? Maybe you don't want to compete with the neighbors on a hot day for a quick dip. Well, get ready to be able to enjoy this slice of heaven right in your own backyard. Open House: Saturday, 11/21 11a-1p; Sunday, 11/22 2p-4p. Stop on by and check this stunning home out!
